snippet.title: MySims – Cozy Bundle Trailer – Nintendo Switch
snippet.description:
MySims: Cozy Bundle is coming to Nintendo Switch on November 19! Pre-order today: https://www.nintendo.com/us/store/products/mysims-cozy-bundle-switch/?utm_source=SW&utm_medium=soytnoa&utm_campaign=P1057-01&utm_id=P1057-01

Make adorable friends and discover creative adventures across retro re-releases of 2 lovable games!  Use your imagination to rebuild a town in MySims, and help a cute magical land become an even better place in MySims Kingdom.
 
#MySims #NintendoDirect #NintendoSwitch

Visit Nintendo.com for more info: https://www.nintendo.com/us/

Subscribe for more Nintendo fun: https://goo.gl/HYYsot
